<div class="about-top">
  <div class="about-us-text">
    <div class="about-header-content">
      We All Love Events!
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="about">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col s12 m12 l12 padding-side-25">
      <h3 class="teal_text">Why Choose Us?</h3>
      <p>We use innovative tools to make sure you create memorable experiences for you and your friends. There are tons of possibilities we believe can be achieved without sweat. Just click a button and we are here to help.</p>
      <div class="why-choose-row">
        <div class="col s12 m12 l4 padding-side-25">
        <div class="bubble teal_bg">
          <div class="bubble-header">1</div>
          <p class="card-title">
            We offer a free service that will never be paid for. We promise...
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m12 l4 padding-side-25">
        <div class="bubble orange_bg">
          <div class="bubble-header">2</div>
          <p class="card-title">
            We also love events! You can count on us to give you updates on the latest events.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m12 l4 padding-side-25">
        <div class="bubble yellow_bg">
          <div class="bubble-header">3</div>
          <p class="card-title">
            We have a great community of event lovers. Share ideas anytime about anything.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

